high_descs: Turn to the right, and then the right again to face the brown table.
Pick up the spatula from the right side of the table.
Hold the spatula and turn to the right and move back to the sink.
Place the spatula in the sink and turn on the water. Turn off the water and pick up the spatula.
Hold the spatula and turn around. Turn to the right at the wall to face the brown table.
Place the spatula on top of the other spatula on the table, towards the front.
anns.task_desc: Rinse a spatula and place it on the table.

high_descs: Turn around to face the brown table.
Pick up the spatula from off of the table.
Turn to the right and go straight to face the sink.
Run the water over the spatula, turn off the water, and pick up the spatula from the sink.
Turn around, go straight and then to the right to face the end of the table.
Place the spatula on the wooden table.
anns.task_desc: Place the rinsed spatula on the wooden table.

high_descs: Turn around to face the table.
Pick up the spatula near the edge of the table.
Turn right and go to the sink in front of you.
Clean the spatula in the sink.
Turn around and go to the wall, then turn right to face the table.
Put the spatula on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean spatula on the table.
